verses.text:
The jubilee has come, return, ye ransomed sinners, home;
The year of jubilee has come, return, ye ransomed sinners, home;
A season of release has come, return, ye ransomed sinners, home.

The trump of jubilee has sounded, the captives shall be free;
The trump of jubilee has sounded, the captives shall be free;
The year of favor has come, return, ye ransomed sinners, home.
